They’re his not mine…
#lab #dogs #labrador

Here at home with Fred he’s getting itchy for the season. It’s funny how a dog can tell certain seasons or feed off there handler/owner but I’ve truly never been more excited to get back in the blind with my boy. The passion shared throughout years and seasons past, bind a mutual love for one thing that only you both get to experience with while providing each other the job well done day after day. He knows he has to please me when working and boy let em tell ya I really don’t brag enough about him. I’ve never loved an animal like I love Fred and in my heart he will never be replaceable.  #mydog #mansbestfriend #labrador #labsofinstagram
These are the best times. He may not know it now but he’ll always remember these days.
